reviewText: Very good quality video and the music was excellent.  I recommend it for all the Ricky Van Shelton Fans.

My mother is in love with Ricky Van Shelton.  He has an amazing voice and can see water out of a well.  Very interesting and entertaining.  My mother can't stop watching and singing along to his hit songs.  More please!
This is a great video and a must for Ricky Van Shelton fans. It has the complete videos of the early, and best, songs that Ricky has done. I love it every single time I watch it.
